                                <p>3.&nbsp;&nbsp;Pull the residue towards the tip of your tongue and then rinse the scraper under the tap.</p>
                                <p>4.&nbsp;&nbsp;Try to scrape as much of the tongue as you can. Around 8 scrapes should be enough.</p>
                                <p>5.&nbsp;&nbsp;Wash the scraper thoroughly, dry it, and put it away for next time.</p>
