                            <p><b>Motivation needs to come from you.</b> It a decision that should be made by you and should be unconditional.</p>
                            <p><br /></p>
                            <p><b>Don't</b> depend on a diet, or a meet-up group, or a family member, or your work schedule.</p>
                            <p><br /></p>
                            <blockquote class="quote" style="text-align:center;">Be <b>PROACTIVE</b>. <i>Make your situation work</i>.</blockquote>
                            <p><br /></p>
                            <p>Whenever you feel motivated,<b> PLAN AHEAD!</b> Make sure you<i> always</i> know the path to follow.</p>
                            <p><br /></p>
