            <H2>3.&nbsp;&nbsp;Make sure you always eat breakfast.</H2>
            <p>
                <br>
            </p>
            <p>Not only can breakfast set the tone for the day, but it can determine the level and subject of your cravings. By eating a good healthy whole-grain breakfast soon after waking up, you will not be hungry during the hours leading up to lunch. </p>
            <p>
                <br>
            </p>
            <p>When you are hungry for a while, you think about food. If you have only just begun eating a whole-grain plant-based diet, this can be a dangerous fork in the road. You may decide you are too hungry to prepare a salad or a stir-fry. You might decide to get an all-day-breakfast fry up or stop off at a fast-food chain.</p>
            <p>
                <br>
            </p>
            <blockquote>Start the day prepared by eating breakfast.</blockquote>

            <p id="fourthd" style="margin-top:-50px;margin-bottom:100px;">
